title: E194 Ross Edgley: The Superhuman Athlete Who Swam Around Great Britain - IMPAULSIVE EP. 194
itunes:title: Ross Edgley: The Superhuman Athlete Who Swam Around Great Britain - IMPAULSIVE EP. 194
description:
Calling in from the UK, endurance athlete Ross Edgley is one of the greatest guests we’ve had on IMPAULSIVE. At 34 years old, he’s climbed a rope the height of Everest, completed a triathlon carrying a 100-pound tree, ran 31 marathons in 31 days, ran 1,000 miles barefoot with a 50kg backpack, and most recently, swam 2,000 miles around England in 157 days. Meet the most durable man in the world.
